Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.01,0:00:01.63,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A wow of silence?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.24,0:00:04.22,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That's err, that's why they asked me to leave
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.97,0:00:06.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I hope it's not a sore subject but,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.38,0:00:10.43,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You mind explaining why you all went quiet in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:12.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's a long story
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.12,0:00:13.48,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,*sigh*
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:15.49,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You'd rather not talk about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:22.82,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,No, I'd rather sing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:24.98,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,La, la-la-la, la la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.26,0:00:27.53,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,La-la-la, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:29.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The Kirin used to speak and sing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:31.05,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We weren't always quiet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.02,0:00:33.78,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We told stories and funny jokes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:35.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,My stand-up was a riot
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.98,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But then one day a fight broke out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.16,0:00:40.82,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And hurtful words were said
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.57,0:00:43.51,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Flaring tempers were inflamed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:45.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Destruction quickly spread
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.03,0:00:48.57,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And flaming bred from head to head
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:50.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Even burnt our bread
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.37,0:00:52.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I forgot how much I love rhyming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.31,0:00:53.49,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Where was I? Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:56.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,My happy village lay in ruins
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.26,0:00:57.77,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Relationships got worse
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:00.68,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Spoiler alert: we quickly learned
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.86,0:01:02.29,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That words could be a curse
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:05.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,"No more talking," yelled our leader
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:07.22,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The last thing said aloud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:09.51,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Into the Stream of Silence
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.87,0:01:12.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We stepped as a crowd
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.35,0:01:14.11,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The water cooled emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.43,0:01:16.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And peace was soon restored
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:18.28,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But with no way to speak my thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:19.97,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I got super bored
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:21.73,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Seriously, there's only so long that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.80,0:01:23.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Sudoku can keep you entertained!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.59,0:01:26.40,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Cause rainbows won't light up the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.57,0:01:28.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Unless you let it rain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.33,0:01:31.82,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And shiny apples sometimes come with worms
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:34.76,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,No, you can't give up yo-ur laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:37.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Cause you're scared of a little pain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:40.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's a lesson that the-e Kirin never learned
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:46.76,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I was stuck in silent pri-ison
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:48.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With the voices in my-y head
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.20,0:01:51.32,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Til I tripped over my-y salvation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.43,0:01:53.05,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,In a helpful flowerbed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:55.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I found a cure to cle-ar my pipes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.03,0:01:57.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And I became quite chatty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:02:00.45,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With years and years of sto-ored-up words
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:02.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I drove my village batty
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:04.94,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,They didn't like my jokes 'n' songs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:06.87,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And daily dose of news
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:09.39,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The plays I wrote, the speeches spoke
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:11.51,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Variety revues
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:13.63,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Or the story about the Kirin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:16.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Who hid below an opera stage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:17.87,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And fell in love with this opera singer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.94,0:02:19.23,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And he wore a freaky half-mask thing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:20.27,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And he played the organ a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:20.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And got all broody
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:22.57,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Because the singer was in love with another dude
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:24.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So he took her away on this underground gondola
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.69,0:02:27.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I mean, who doesn't love musical theater?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.03,0:02:30.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The village leader made it clear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:31.87,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I had to make my choice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:34.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I could stay and live with them
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:36.47,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Or I could keep my voice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:39.81,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So I came here, but left the couch alo-one
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:41.10,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,They're hard to move
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:43.73,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With just the view for company
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:45.81,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Until ya heard me gro-ove
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:47.46,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Take it away, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:48.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.62,0:02:52.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Cause rainbows won't light up the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:54.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Unless you let it rain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:57.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Candles just won't glow until they're burned
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:00.86,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,No, you can't give up yo-ur laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:03.12,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Cause you're scared of a little pain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:07.18,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's a lesson that my-y village never learned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:11.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard I schooled them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:13.61,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Fear of hu-urt is still what ruled them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:20.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you gotta le-et it rain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:26.54,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sometimes you've gotta let it ra-in
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:30.60,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Cause rainbows won't light up the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:32.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Unless you let it rain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:35.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And candles just won't glow until they're burned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.17,0:03:39.08,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,No, you can't give up yo-ur laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.22,0:03:41.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,'Cause you're scared of a little pain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:45.43,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's a lesson that my-y village never learned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:49.24,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, 'cause rainbows won't light up the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:50.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Unless you letit
